类 IEEE754

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.wuqinxuan.numbercruncher.mathutils.IEEE754
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IEEE754Constants

    public class IEEE754
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEEE754Constants
    Decompose a floating-point value into its parts according to the IEEE 754 standard.
